resources UK(42)
notes
Tristatic UHF and Fabry-Perot Interferometer (FPI) observations of ion and 
neutral flow in the upper and lower thermosphere. The objection is to study 
meso-scale variability of the ion-neutral coupling. Clear sky is required at 
Kiruna, Ramfjord and Sodankyla. Cancellations are anticipated. The UHF-
tristatic will run a standard code, e.g. beata. 

